Casting for the Trailer of upcoming novel "Tres Leches"

 

AntLive Movement LLC is currently casting for its three main characters for Tres Leches Web series. We will be shooting the pilot episode of the web series which involves a love scene. Looking for passionate, adventurous and outgoing individuals that can spark great chemistry with the other actors. The goal is for this series to be a soap opera that will run on the AntLive Movement website with some episodes on YouTube. It's a three-book series being turn into a web series. We are technically starting the web series in the middle of the story, the heart and middle piece of the entire series.

The Umbrella of the Tres Leches story is an agency that creates traditional housewives that been in business since the 1930s. But the first book focus on Ciara Taylor and how the agency has influenced her life. The story is about A young, black and married Ciara Taylor Scott, who is on the cusp of making history as the first black female mayor of Detroit when she becomes entangled in an unexpected love affair with two of her biggest supporters--her best friend, Valerie Brock, and her high school sweetheart, Rafael Delgado. Still trying to escape from under her father's shadow, Ciara learns that her father, the former mayor of Detroit, will be released from prison after 20 years. As the passions of her past haunt her and the fear of her future grows, Ciara must determine which path to follow on the campaign trail toward the mayoral seat: the one led by her heart, the one led by her mind, or the one led by the euphoria between her legs.

The pilot is in the woods as Ciara is walking through the woods, its greeny smoky seductive vibe that catches the audience attention in what Ciara is thinking about as she is walking through the woods. As she is walking through the woods she sees reflections and encounters with her loves ones, Ciara, Rafael holding each other in an exotic position on a bed, another scene involving Valerie. Ciara speaking in front of thousands of Detroit Residents in a town hall setting and much more scenes through the series she is reminiscing as she continues walking through the woods.

CHARACTERS:

Valerie Delgado: A beautiful gorgeous Looking Latino woman with spontaneous and outgoing personality

Skin colour: Smooth Ivory Skin

Eyes: Delvish Red

Body: Tone fit body sexy Latina firecracker

Hair: Blonde or Black

Height: Between 5'9 and 6'2

Age Range: Between late 20's and early 30's

Occupation: Dance/Actor

Ciara Taylor Scott - A beautiful black woman who is ambitious and dedicated and at times can be mind control by her BFF Valerie.

Skin colour: Dark Carmel tone complication

Hair: Black (Short or Long) willing to see both styles

Height: 5'8 to 6'0

Body: Tone fit body, sexy athletic type, use to run track in high school.

Age Range: late 20's early 30's

Occupation: Runs a Non-Profit Organization Detroit 20/20 and is running for Mayor (First black female if elected)

Rafael Delgado - A Latino Male with a great smile and captivating dimples. Very spiritual and close to his mother

Skin colour: Brown tone complication

Height: Between 6'1 and 6'2

Body: Slim/Muscular type body has nice abs but the 6 pack is not that visible. (Sexy muscular pecks are a must not flat chest)

Age Range: Between late 20's and early 30's

Occupation: Psychiatrist (Graduate from Puerto Rico)

Production Date: TBA

Location: A presidential suite hotel (Location of hotel to be announced)

Audition: Email and will schedule date and time

Note: The goal is to have 4 different sets of Trio characters. All 12 characters will attend at the same time and we will do a live taping. There will be food in the lobby waiting for area where actors can mix and mingle practice each other's line with one another. The whole audition will last between 2 to 3 hours may get sent home early if we have seen enough takes of you.

Note: When you submit your request A script of the scene that you will be rehearsing will be sent to you via email

IMPORTANT: TO RECEIVE THE SCRIPT, YOU MUST SEND AT LEAST THREE OF YOUR BEST PHOTO'S

Not required but recommended: Any video's you may have of you acting, it can be a link to a YouTube video or a file.

Compensation:

Pay Out: $200.00 (12-hour shoot) (More than likely wont need you the whole day on some characters)

Food and beverage will be provided at the shoot

Contact
Name: Antoine Jennings
Phone Number: 313-401-1813
Email: Antoinelive1984@gmail.com
Website:treslechesnovel.com
